  "ai_usage": "Use for nostalgia projects, 404 easter eggs, or retro-themed events. Copy the document and edit the name/bio/counter. It deliberately evokes GeoCities but avoids deprecated tags and seizure risks: the marquee is CSS (pauses on hover, stops under reduced-motion). Treat the patterns as a costume, not best practice.",
